snippet.textDisplay:
Sabko pta rehta hai ki buton mein khuda nhi hota, pr jb humare beech humare bhgwan,paigambar nahi hai- unko yaad krne ke liye, unko izzat dene ke liye, aane waali pediyon ko ye btane ke liye ki aisi bhi society exist krti thi- buton,masjid,mandir,girjaghar,gurudwara ki zaroorat rehti hai.Ek aam thake hue aadmi ko apne man ki saari shikayatein, saara dukh, saara maange us buth ko de aata hai, usse pta rehta hai ki ye pathar ka tukda hai pr fir bhi vishwas rehta hai ki nizam-e-hasti chala raha hai, jo din ko raat, raat ko din bna rha hai,wahi khuda hai aur wo exist krta hai..!!

4 deewaron se ghr nhi bnta, rehne walo ki feelings se bnta hai, waise hi kisi bhi buth ki importance- unke anuwayion ke liye hota hai, warna hum aap matter ke bane hai kisi cheez ka koi mol nahi hota sab kuch referencial hai, cheezon ki keemat hum tey krte hai.
1000 ke note ki keemat 10 bhi ho skti thi aur 10 ki 1000.
